## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="19219-102">根據預設，<xref:System.Object>型別引數會封送處理為`VARIANT`型別，其中的物件型別會決定`VARTYPE`的值`VARIANT`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="19219-102">By default, <xref:System.Object> type arguments are marshaled as a `VARIANT` type, where the object type determines the `VARTYPE` value of the `VARIANT`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="19219-103"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>輸入要做為傳遞必須<xref:System.Object>封送處理成的型別`VARIANT`型別的`VT_ERROR`，否則為<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>類型會封送處理為整數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="19219-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type must to be passed as an <xref:System.Object> type to be marshaled as a `VARIANT` of type `VT_ERROR`, otherwise the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type is marshaled as an integer.</span></span>  
  
